

### Hidden Valley packet
### Kroger packet


### Nytimes
### P. 612

* 1 cup mayonnaise
* 1/2 cup buttermilk
* 1/4 cup buttermilk powder
* salt + pepper
* 1/4 cup chopped chives / parsley

* combine mayo, buttermilk, buttermilk powder in a jar with tight-fitting lid
* sprinkle salt + pepper
* shake vigorously for 30 seconds
* keeps longer without herbs


### Fearing
### Jalapeno Ranch p. 35

* 1 cup buttermilk
* 1/2 cup mayo
* 1/2 cup chopped jalapeno chile
* 1 ounce ranch dressing mix
* tabasco
* lime juice
